File: platform/plugin-tools/src/commands/build.ts, lines 1100-1111. Currently:

  await writeFile(iifePath, ...);
  if (await access(iifePath).then(() => true, () => false)) {
    const iifeSize = (await stat(iifePath)).size;
    console.log(`  Written: ...`);
  } else {
    console.log(pc.dim(`  dist/${ADAPTER_FILENAME} not generated`));
  }

The access check always succeeds because writeFile just wrote the file. Replace with:

  await writeFile(iifePath, ...);
  const iifeSize = (await stat(iifePath)).size;
  console.log(`  Written: ${pc.bold(`dist/${ADAPTER_FILENAME}`)} (${formatBytes(iifeSize)})`);

Note: the source map check on lines 1113-1126 should be LEFT ALONE — the source map file is produced by esbuild, and it's legitimate to check whether it exists (esbuild might not generate it in all configurations).
